<section>
<h2>De decimal a base $b$</h2>
Convertir $61_{(10}$ a base $3$
<table>
<tr><td>Número</td><td>Número/3</td><td>Resto</td></tr>
<tr><td class="fragment">61</td><td class="fragment">20</td><td class="fragment post_it">1</td></tr>

<tr><td class="fragment">20</td><td class="fragment">6</td><td class="fragment post_it">2</td></tr>
<tr><td class="fragment">6</td><td class="fragment post_it">2</td><td class="fragment post_it">0</td></tr>
<tr></tr>
</table>
<p>
<span class="fragment">$61_{(10} = 2 * 3^3 + 0 * 3^2 + 2 * 3 + 1$ </span>
</p>
<span class="fragment">$61_{(10} = 2021_{(3}$ </span>
</section>

